msgstr "التوقيت العالمي"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"[List of tz database time "
"zones](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_tz_database_time_zones)"
msgstr ""
"[قائمة المناطق الزمنية لقاعدة بيانات "
"tz](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_tz_database_time_zones)"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
